comments: This contract was competitively sourced.To assist us in the modernization project and in the introduction of new softwares while doing so, a Publication Support Coordinator was hired as a temporary help to provide the support required to continue to publish on time Parts I, II, III, the special editions, the Quarterly Index and the Consolidated Index of the Canada Gazette. This contract was obtained through a Supply Arrangement at PWGSC and was competitively sourced.
